&lt;h2&gt;Administrador(a) de Vendas&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Sao Paulo, Brasil&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Visão Geral da Posição&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;O(A) Administrador(a) de Vendas apoia a equipe comercial por meio da gestão de atividades administrativas, manutenção de dados de clientes, coordenação de processos de vendas e garantia de fluxos operacionais eficientes. Esta função desempenha um papel fundamental na melhoria da eficiência comercial e na entrega de uma experiência de alta qualidade ao cliente.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Principais Responsabilidades&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Suporte às Vendas&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul data-spread=&quot;false&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Auxiliar a equipe de vendas na preparação de cotações, propostas e contratos.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Processar pedidos, acompanhar entregas e garantir o cumprimento dos prazos.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manter registros atualizados das interações com clientes nos sistemas de CRM.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordenar com equipes internas (Financeiro, Logística e Marketing) para apoiar as atividades comerciais.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Dados e Relatórios&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul data-spread=&quot;false&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Gerar relatórios periódicos de vendas, dashboards e indicadores de desempenho.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analisar dados de vendas para identificar tendências e apoiar a tomada de decisões.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manter e atualizar preços de produtos, cadastros de clientes e bases de dados comerciais.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Atendimento ao Cliente&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul data-spread=&quot;false&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Atuar como ponto de contato para dúvidas de clientes e atualizações sobre o status de pedidos.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Tratar solicitações e problemas dos clientes, realizando escalonamentos quando necessário.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Garantir altos níveis de satisfação dos clientes por meio de respostas ágeis e eficazes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Otimização de Processos&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul data-spread=&quot;false&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identificar oportunidades para aprimorar processos comerciais e fluxos administrativos.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Apoiar a implementação de novas ferramentas, sistemas ou tecnologias.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;IA e Tecnologia (Desejável)&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul data-spread=&quot;false&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conhecimento básico de conceitos e ferramentas de Inteligência Artificial (IA).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experiência com ferramentas baseadas em IA para análise de vendas, previsões ou geração de insights sobre clientes será considerada um diferencial.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiaridade com plataformas de CRM que possuam recursos de IA (ex.: Dynamics 365, Salesforce Einstein).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Capacidade de utilizar ferramentas de automação para aumentar a eficiência e reduzir atividades manuais.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Qualificações&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Formação Acadêmica&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul data-spread=&quot;false&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Graduação em Administração de Empresas, Vendas, Marketing ou áreas correlatas (desejável).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Experiência&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul data-spread=&quot;false&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Entre 2 e 5 anos de experiência em funções de administração ou suporte de vendas.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experiência com sistemas CRM e ferramentas de apoio comercial.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Competências&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul data-spread=&quot;false&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Forte capacidade de organização e gestão de múltiplas tarefas.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excelente comunicação e habilidades interpessoais.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiência no Microsoft Office (Excel, PowerPoint e Word).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perfil analítico com atenção aos detalhes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Capacidade de trabalhar de forma colaborativa em um ambiente dinâmico e de ritmo acelerado.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Competências Desejáveis&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul data-spread=&quot;fa

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job Summary&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In this role you will be expected to provide administrative assistance for the business and be willing to go above and beyond daily.&amp;nbsp; You will take ownership of delegated tasks and ensure they are completed in a timely and orderly manner, to a high standard. You will have high attention to detail and a can do, proactive attitude.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The duties initially assigned include, but are not limited to:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reception relief (cover for lunch, breaks and Friday afternoon from 3pm)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assistance organising and preparing for internal staff events&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Daily Staff Movements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Co-ordination of meetings, conference calls and video conferences with both internal &amp;amp; external stakeholders&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Preparing documents/presentations – formatting, printing, binding as needed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assistance with monthly Amex reconciliation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Other shared responsibilities (with Admin Team)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Responding to requests via team inbox&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Co-ordination of travel – Domestic&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;WorkDay Expense reconciliation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;ASG Team support and role coverage&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Experience and Qualifications&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3-5 years’ experience as an Administrative Assistant within a corporate environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Qualifications in Office / Business Administration desirable&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to work in a team environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Advanced skills in Microsoft Office; Outlook and established applications&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Advanced skills in Microsoft 365 and Workday would be desirable&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About InterSystems&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;InterSystems, a creative data technology provider, delivers a unified foundation for next-generation applications for healthcare, finance, manufacturing, and supply chain customers in more than 80 countries. Our data platforms solve interoperability, speed, and scalability problems for large organizations around the globe to unlock the power of data and allow people to perceive data in imaginative ways. Established in 1978, InterSystems is committed to excellence through its 24×7 support for customers and partners around the world. Privately held and headquartered in Boston, Massachusetts, InterSystems has 38 offices in 28 countries worldwide. For more information, please visit&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://cts.businesswire.com/ct/CT?id=smartlink&amp;amp;url=https://www.intersystems.com/&amp;amp;esheet=53379223&amp;amp;newsitemid=20230410005415&amp;amp;lan=en-US&amp;amp;anchor=InterSystems.com&amp;amp;index=4&amp;amp;md5=3edf749fa33f5a2ac0c355c410576e90&quot; data-outlook-id=&quot;1e721f69-f681-4067-9281-970e94b3ef11&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;InterSystems.com&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Administrative Assistant&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;InterSystems Corporation is a privately held software company with a 40-year track record of consistent growth and profitability. We view hiring, developing, and retaining the best people as key to our record of success.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;Job Summary:&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Provide PA and Administrative support for Senior Management and administrative support on an as-needed basis for other areas of the business.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;Job Responsibilities:&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;PA support, including arranging internal and external meetings, booking travel, gatekeeping, processing expenses, etc&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;General admin support to the teams including organising flight, hotel and taxi bookings through a dedicated travel agency&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Attendance at meetings which require preparation of agendas, collation of reports and the taking of accurate minutes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Arranging ad-hoc meetings, sometimes off-site, including organising catering&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Raising purchase orders&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Tracking team travel and approval of invoices&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Project support during implementation period including document management, control of project intranet page (SharePoint), minute taking at project reviews&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reception cover for full time receptionist during breaks/holidays etc. (shared with rest of Administrative Services Group (ASG))&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;General support as part of ASG team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide additional cover for other administrative staff during absences or when assisting with specific projects and ad-hoc tasks&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist in the organisation/coordination of Company events&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Act on behalf of the team as a liaison between internal departments, offices and customers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;Required Skills and Experience:&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Previous Admin/PA experience is essential, preferably in an international company&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience of supporting multiple managers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of supporting a Sales team is desirable&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong administration, planning and organisational skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Good written and oral communication&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to produce accurate and professional written documentation, particularly on MS Word&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience using AI-powered productivity tools such as Microsoft 365 Copilot, ChatGPT, or similar platforms to support document creation, data analysis, presentation development, meeting preparation, and administrative workflows.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to write clear, effective prompts and instructions to generate accurate, relevant, and business-appropriate outputs from AI systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to evaluate, verify, and refine AI-generated content to ensure accuracy, professionalism, confidentiality, and alignment with business requirements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong understanding of responsible AI usage, including data privacy, information security, and appropriate handling of confidential business information.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Self-starter who can be proactive and forward thinking but can also react quickly to urgent situations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Good working knowledge of MS Word, Excel, Outlook, and PowerPoint&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of SharePoint advantageous&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Previous project support beneficial&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to multi-task&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About InterSystems&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;InterSystems, a creative data technolo

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job Summary&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Application Specialist will contribute to the successful and timely deployment of the TrakCare product by providing application knowledge and product delivery services in the functional areas of product implementation, requirements scoping, field design documentation and change request testing.&amp;nbsp; Spending up to 50% of their time working directly from customer sites and other InterSystems offices, the Application Specialist will act as an “expert” product resource for customers and will be expected to communicate and prioritize customer requirements to other areas of the business.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Liaise with customers in order to understand the work processes and requirements that are required to be addressed by the TrakCare application&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Implement the TrakCare application in a manner that will suit the business requirements of the customer and follow the methodologies and processes of InterSystems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct individual and group training, product demonstrations and workshops as required&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Implement and control change management requests from client&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deliver successful application implementation phases&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be a Subject Matter Expert (SME) for TrakCare implementations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;If required, work with customers to identify potential changes within the parameters of the product&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Other duties may be directed by the Company from time to time.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Experience and Qualifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Understanding and experience with Hospital Information, Patient Administration (PAS), and Clinical Information Systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Clinical (Nursing, eMeds) or Patient Administration Systems (PAS) preferred&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Understanding of the importance of Health Informatics standards, reporting requirements and legislative controls&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;General aptitude for solving problems and using technology to improve processes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Understanding and experience in implementation of product solutions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A solid grasp of computer systems, software development and deployment methodology and computer networking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;An ability to handle multiple tasks simultaneously and within tight time constraints&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven ability to think laterally and come up with innovative solutions for software product implementations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The ability to make independent recommendations for successful software product implementations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven ability to work through problems with different customer groups achieving positive outcomes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The ability to spend up to 50% of time travelling and working from customer sites and other InterSystems offices&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Education and Training&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Health Information or Clinical University Degree&lt;/p&gt;
