&lt;p&gt;InterSystems UKI have a Graduate opportunity for an Application Specialist role to work within the experienced and highly skilled TrakCare Laboratory Enterprise (TCLE) team.&amp;nbsp; The TCLE implementation team delivers TCLE to Clinical Laboratories which provides tools and reports to support the entire life cycle of lab services, delivery and workload across the enterprise.&lt;/p&gt;
