&lt;li&gt;Provide pragmatic contractual advice to support sales and project mobilisation activities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Post-Contract Management&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage contracts following signature, including business adherence to contractual obligations, change control processes and contract variations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support the delivery and operations teams in the practical application and management of contractual obligations throughout the contract lifecycle.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor contractual performance, compliance and key post-signature obligations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support the management of third-party vendors/sub-contractors and suppliers, both local and global, as required.&lt;/li&gt;
