&lt;li&gt;Implement and ensure adherence to internal contract management and governance processes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage ambiguity and develop practical, proportionate solutions to contractual and risk management challenges.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Stakeholder Engagement&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide clear, practical guidance on contractual matters to colleagues at all levels, including the Legal, Sales, Delivery and Leadership teams.&lt;/li&gt;
